The purpose of Unit 9 Offplot is to store and transfer raw streams, intermediates and products, both between process units and the outside. Product is stored in tanks, bullets, and spheres. Tanks are connected to the Marine Terminal, the process units, crude oil pipelines, and the finished product pipeline. There are many interconnecting lines to allow receipts, transfers, and deliveries. The LPG area including LPG railcars, Slops tanks (300x35 and 100x92), and Pentaref tanks (550x102 and 550x106) are covered under RMP.

